dkeep.logic

Class Dungeon

  • java.lang.Object
    • dkeep.logic.Dungeon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameLogic, java.io.Serializable

    public class Dungeon
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameLogic, java.io.Serializable
    Abstraction of the Dungeon level in game: It allows to move the hero, the guard, to pick a type of guard or for it to be randomly picked and to check the game's status
    See Also:
